<p>Cryptocurrency is a digital currency that allows quick and secure online payments. It doesn&#39;t rely on banks to verify transactions and enables anyone anywhere to send and receive payments.</p>

<p>In the below countries, FARFETCH accepts cryptocurrency as a direct payment method at checkout.</p>

